                            <h1>Welcome to the CSLP!</h1>
              <p>The Centre for the Study of Learning and Performance is a multi-institutional research centre of excellence composed of dozens of faculty researchers, a diverse professional staff, and a large number of graduate students.</p>
                          </div>
            <div> <span class="jFlowControl"></span> <img width="848" height="250" src="http://doe.concordia.ca/cslp/cslp_cms/sites/all/themes/jframe/images/img2.jpg" class="attachment-home-feature wp-post-image" />
                            <h1>Members</h1>
              <p>Researchers work with a number of collaborators and associates from across Canada and around the world.</p>
                          </div>
            <div> <span class="jFlowControl"></span> <img width="848" height="250" src="http://doe.concordia.ca/cslp/cslp_cms/sites/all/themes/jframe/images/img3.jpg" class="attachment-home-feature wp-post-image" />
                            <h1>Organizations</h1>
              <p>Our Centre also enjoys active partnerships with a range of individuals and organizations in the educational community who contribute to our research and help to actively disseminate the results of our projects.</p>
                          </div>
