      <h2><a href="/cslp/cslp_cms/?q=node/484" title="Congratulations to Dr. Robert Bernard">Congratulations to Dr. Robert Bernard</a></h2>
  
      <span class="submitted">Mon, 03/30/2015 - 14:29</span>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Congratulations to Dr. Robert Bernard, who was chosen as an Outstanding Reviewer for 2014 by the American Educational Research Association (AERA) and the Review of Educational Research (RER). He will be recognized for his extraordinary service at the Journal Publications Committee Reception at the AERA annual meeting in Chicago on Thursday April 16th, 2015.</p>
  </div>

