<div id="node-477" class="node">

  
      <h2><a href="/cslp/cslp_cms/?q=node/477" title="LTK+ News">LTK+ News</a></h2>
  
      <span class="submitted">Fri, 02/13/2015 - 13:30</span>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>The CSLP is very pleased to announce the upcoming release of the <strong>LTK+</strong> in the Fall 2015. This important release will include the long awaited French adaptation of <strong>ABRACADABRA</strong>, the first version of <strong>ELM</strong>: Emerging Literacy in Mathematics and an updated version of <strong>READS</strong>: A repository of free digital stories.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="meta clearfix">

   
    
  </div>

</div>
      </div> <!-- /#main -->
      </div>
      
    <div id="right">
      <div id="text-9" class="widgets">
       <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
        <div style="font-size:20px; font-weight:normal; color:#619ce4; font-family:Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; float:left; margin-top:3px; width:100%; margin-bottom:10px; border-bottom: solid 4px #f3f0ed; padding-bottom:11px; width:270px;">
                	CSLP Spotlight
                </div>
      </div>
			<h4>READS is now available!</h4>
			<p><img src="/cslp/cslp_cms/sites/all/themes/jframe/images/reads.png" style="margin-bottom: 7px;"/><br>Accessible from the LTK Lobby page, READS is a repository of over 450 free digital stories in 27 different languages. These engaging stories geared primarily for beginning readers have been catalogued by theme, genre, reading level, country of origin and language. Designed to complement the fluency and comprehension activities within ABRACADABRA, the database will continue to grow as we gather permissions from authors and publishers. Check it out in our latest release of the LTK.</p>			
			<a href="/cslp/cslp_cms/?q=node/118"><img src="/cslp/cslp_cms/sites/all/themes/jframe/images/ltkbtn_2.jpg" /></a>
			<br>
			<span style="font-size: 10px;margin-top:15px;margin-right:10px;float:right;margin-bottom:15px"><a href="/cslp/cslp_cms/?q=node/325">Archives</a> &#187;</span>
			<br><br>
			<h4>Overview of the CSLP Educational Technology Theme</h4>
			<!-- player container-->
